Type
====

* /type [GET, POST] - collection of types
* /type/<type_id/type_name> [DELETE, GET, PUT] - detailed type information
* /type/<type_id/type_name>/item [GET] - collection of items with given type

Items
=====

* /item [GET, POST] - collection of items
* /item/<item_id> [DELETE, GET, PUT] - detailed item information
* /item/<item_id>/image [GET, POST] - item image collection.  POST expects a HTML form

Makers
======

* /maker [GET, POST] - collection of makers
* /maker/<maker_id> [DELETE, GET, PUT] - detailed maker information
* /maker/<maker_id>/item [GET] - collection of items made by maker

Browse by Year
==============

* /year/<year>/item [GET] - collection of items

Attachments
===========

* /attachment/<attachment_id> [GET] - download the attachment file
* /attachment/<attachment_id>/image/<width>x<height> [GET] - download a scaled image
* /attachment/<attachment_id>/info [DELETE, GET, PUT] - attachment metadata

Options
=======

* /option [GET, PUT] - get all options or update multiple options (options not set in a PUT will be left)
* /option/<option_name> [DELETE, GET, PUT] - delete, get or update a single option

